text: Julian Hussauf (born April 8, 2006 in Rottenmann) is an Austrian football player. He plays as defender for the Second league team FC Liefering. == Career == Hussauf began his career at FC Gaishorn. For the 2017/18 season he moved to SK Sturm Graz. For the 2019/20 season he moved to the youth team of FC Red Bull Salzburg. He went through all age levels in the academy from the 2020/21 season. For the 2024/25 season, Hussauf moved into the squad of FC Liefering. FC Liefering Homepage He made his debut in the 2nd league in August 2024. He came on as a substitute for Gaoussou Diakit√© against SV Lafnitz. FC Salzburg Wiki == International == Hussauf made his debut for the Austrian U-18 team in March 2024 against Italy.
